{
  "stem": "23438.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But somehow or else, we did, under the pretense that we were the nursing staff to look after the refugees.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They were just sort of empty train wagons with just little folding beds, sort of two pieces of timber and a piece of denim in between.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We went through Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We stopped for a day in Prague.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was a very beautiful experience for me, because I had never been outside Poland's borders before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We went through Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We stopped on the French border in a DP's camp, a camp for Displaced Persons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And there we were told, not going any further, not going to France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I went to a beg the camp commander.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I told him I had an uncle in France and he wanted me to go to his place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took my uncle's name and address, Uncle lived then in Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he sent him a wire, asking whether it was true that he wanted me to stay with him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Uncle confirmed that, so I was allowed to leave and I was put on a train to Paris.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a day's break, waiting for a nice night train to Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember where I had the money to pay for tickets, whether there were any tickets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What I remember was that I was in Paris and I was hungry and I couldn't buy any food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were stalls with beautiful sandwiches on pieces of French sticks in all metro stations or in the streets.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you had to have coupons to buy them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't have any coupons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was still a very illegal citizen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I ended by-- I ended up buying a pound of fresh dates.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
